{"tid":2235954,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中銀粉嶺分行遭示威者破壞 事隔一年四青年被控今提堂","createTime":"2020-10-09T05:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T06:24:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f94d97f06bcc874d37184d5c20e3109bf17f7af","tid":2235954,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"反修例運動去年爆發以來，本港中資銀行不時成為示威者「裝修」目標。去年10月，粉嶺中國銀行分行疑遭示威者破壞。三男一女被指當日參與破壞及管有雷射筆，當中三人為未成年學生。事隔一年，四名青年被控非法集結及刑事損壞等罪，今在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。主任裁判官蘇文隆將案件押後至12月3日再訊，並批准被告各以5,000元保釋候訊，其間須宵禁及不准離港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/DA4LKP2AUZB75A45DNZ4ND5GDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FDA4LKP2AUZB75A45DNZ4ND5GDA%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=05141da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FDA4LKP2AUZB75A45DNZ4ND5GDA%2F&h=18081b66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/DA4LKP2AUZB75A45DNZ4ND5GDA/</a>"},{"pid":"9ad660698d4f29af10e7ff70e40ae043a11ec3c9","tid":2235954,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428e005fab3b27fa615c992c190947def6a05483","tid":2235954,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:11:42.000Z","msg":"又係未成年學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f44e3c649e6a8ab72ac2b4990142f17cafb212a","tid":2235954,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31960f98596f0744724e674b942f67226046a1ec","tid":2235954,"uid":11291,"like"